  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if intravenous micronutrient therapy (IVMT) is
      effective in the treatment of fibromyalgia, as assessed by validated functional and pain
      measures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
